quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  26,84,wajel li thna' hsnana wdhkrana jamilaan fi aladhin yatun baedi 'iilaa yawm alqyamt
  26,85,wajelny min eibadik aladhin twrthhm naeim aljnt
  26,86,"whdha duea' min 'iibrahim ealayh alslam 'an yunqidh allah 'abah min aldalal 'iilaa alhda, fayaghfir lah wytjawz enh, kama waead 'iibrahim 'abah baldea' lh, falamaa tbyan lah 'anah mustamirun fi alkufr walshrk 'iilaa 'ana yamut tbrra mnh"
  26,87,"wla tulhq bi aldhl, yawm yakhruj alnaas min alqubur llhsab waljza', yawm la yanfae almal walbanun ahdana min alebad, 'iilaa man 'ataa allah biqalb salim min alkufr walnfaq walrdhylt"
  26,88,"wla tulhq bi aldhl, yawm yakhruj alnaas min alqubur llhsab waljza', yawm la yanfae almal walbanun ahdana min alebad, 'iilaa man 'ataa allah biqalb salim min alkufr walnfaq walrdhylt"
  26,89,"wla tulhq bi aldhl, yawm yakhruj alnaas min alqubur llhsab waljza', yawm la yanfae almal walbanun ahdana min alebad, 'iilaa man 'ataa allah biqalb salim min alkufr walnfaq walrdhylt"
  26,90,"wqurribt aljanat liladhin ajtanibuu alkufr walmeasy, wa'aqbaluu ealaa allah baltaet"
  26,91,"w'uzhrt alnaar lilkafirin aladhin dallu ean alhda, wtjrrawu ealaa mharm allah wkdhdhabu rslh"
  26,92,"wqyl lahum twbykhana: 'ayn alihatakum alati kuntum tebdwnha min dun allh, wtzemwn 'anaha tshfe lakum alywm? hal ynsrwnkm, fydfewn aleadhab enkm, 'aw yantasirun bidafe aleadhab ean anfshm? la shay' min dhlk"
  26,93,"wqyl lahum twbykhana: 'ayn alihatakum alati kuntum tebdwnha min dun allh, wtzemwn 'anaha tshfe lakum alywm? hal ynsrwnkm, fydfewn aleadhab enkm, 'aw yantasirun bidafe aleadhab ean anfshm? la shay' min dhlk"
  26,94,"fjumieu walquu fi jhnm, hum waladhin adlwhm waewan 'iiblis aladhin zyanu lahum alshr, lm yuflit minhum ahd"
  26,95,"fjumieu walquu fi jhnm, hum waladhin adlwhm waewan 'iiblis aladhin zyanu lahum alshr, lm yuflit minhum ahd"
  26,96,"qalu metrfyn bkhtyhm, wahum yatanazaeun fi jahanam mae man adlwhm, tallah 'iinana kunna fi aldunya fi dalal wadih la khfa' fyh; 'iidh nusawiykum birabi alealamin almsthq llebadt whdh. wama awqena fi hadha almasir alsyiy 'iilaa almujrimun aladhin daeuna 'iilaa eibadat ghayr allah fatbenahm"
  26,97,"qalu metrfyn bkhtyhm, wahum yatanazaeun fi jahanam mae man adlwhm, tallah 'iinana kunna fi aldunya fi dalal wadih la khfa' fyh; 'iidh nusawiykum birabi alealamin almsthq llebadt whdh. wama awqena fi hadha almasir alsyiy 'iilaa almujrimun aladhin daeuna 'iilaa eibadat ghayr allah fatbenahm"
  26,98,"qalu metrfyn bkhtyhm, wahum yatanazaeun fi jahanam mae man adlwhm, tallah 'iinana kunna fi aldunya fi dalal wadih la khfa' fyh; 'iidh nusawiykum birabi alealamin almsthq llebadt whdh. wama awqena fi hadha almasir alsyiy 'iilaa almujrimun aladhin daeuna 'iilaa eibadat ghayr allah fatbenahm"
  26,99,"qalu metrfyn bkhtyhm, wahum yatanazaeun fi jahanam mae man adlwhm, tallah 'iinana kunna fi aldunya fi dalal wadih la khfa' fyh; 'iidh nusawiykum birabi alealamin almsthq llebadt whdh. wama awqena fi hadha almasir alsyiy 'iilaa almujrimun aladhin daeuna 'iilaa eibadat ghayr allah fatbenahm"
  26,100,"fla ahd yashfae lna, wykhllisna min aledhab, wala man yasduq fi mwdtna wyshfq elyna"
  26,101,"fla ahd yashfae lna, wykhllisna min aledhab, wala man yasduq fi mwdtna wyshfq elyna"
  26,102,"flyt lana rjet 'iilaa aldnya, fnsyr min jumlatan almuminin alnajyn"
  26,103,"'in fi naba 'iibrahim alssabiq laebrt limn yetbr, wama sar 'akthar aladhin samieuu hdha alnaba mwmnyn. wa'iina rabak lahu aleaziz alqadir ealaa alantqam min almkdhbyn, alrahim bieibadih almwmnyn"
  26,104,"'iina fi naba 'iibrahim alssabiq laebrt limn yetbr, wama sar 'akthar aladhin samieuu hdha alnaba mwmnyn. wa'iina rabak lahu aleaziz alqadir ealaa alantqam min almkdhbyn, alrahim bieibadih almwmnyn"
  26,105,"kadhdhabt qawm nuh risalatan nbyhm, fakanuu bhdha mukadhibin lajamie alrsl; li'ana kl rasul yamur btsdyq jmye alrsl. 'iidh qal lahum 'akhuhum nwh: 'alaa takhshawn allah bitark eibadat ghyrh? 'iiniy lakum rasul 'amin fima ablghkm, fajelu al'iiman wqayt lakum min eadhab allah watyewny fima amrkm bih min eibadatih whdh. wama 'atlub minkum ajrana ealaa tblygh alrsalt, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn, almtsrf fi khlqh, fahdharuu eqabh, watyewny bamtthal awamrh, wajtnab nwahyh"
  26,106,"kadhdhabt qawm nuh risalatan nbyhm, fakanuu bhdha mukadhibin lajamie alrsl; li'ana kl rasul yamur btsdyq jmye alrsl. 'iidh qal lahum 'akhuhum nwh: 'alaa takhshawn allah bitark eibadat ghyrh? 'iiniy lakum rasul 'amin fima ablghkm, fajelu al'iiman wqayt lakum min eadhab allah watyewny fima amrkm bih min eibadatih whdh. wama 'atlub minkum ajrana ealaa tblygh alrsalt, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn, almtsrf fi khlqh, fahdharuu eqabh, watyewny bamtthal awamrh, wajtnab nwahyh"
  26,107,"kadhdhabt qawm nuh risalatan nbyhm, fakanuu bhdha mukadhibin lajamie alrsl; li'ana kl rasul yamur btsdyq jmye alrsl. 'iidh qal lahum 'akhuhum nwh: 'alaa takhshawn allah bitark eibadat ghyrh? 'iiniy lakum rasul 'amin fima ablghkm, fajelu al'iiman wqayt lakum min eadhab allah watyewny fima amrkm bih min eibadatih whdh. wama 'atlub minkum ajrana ealaa tblygh alrsalt, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn, almtsrf fi khlqh, fahdharuu eqabh, watyewny bamtthal awamrh, wajtnab nwahyh"
  26,108,"kadhdhabt qawm nuh risalatan nbyhm, fakanuu bhdha mukadhibin lajamie alrsl; li'ana kl rasul yamur btsdyq jmye alrsl. 'iidh qal lahum 'akhuhum nwh: 'alaa takhshawn allah bitark eibadat ghyrh? 'iiniy lakum rasul 'amin fima ablghkm, fajelu al'iiman wqayt lakum min eadhab allah watyewny fima amrkm bih min eibadatih whdh. wama 'atlub minkum ajrana ealaa tblygh alrsalt, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn, almtsrf fi khlqh, fahdharuu eqabh, watyewny bamtthal awamrh, wajtnab nwahyh"
  26,109,"kadhdhabt qawm nuh risalatan nbyhm, fakanuu bhdha mukadhibin lajamie alrsl; li'ana kl rasul yamur btsdyq jmye alrsl. 'iidh qal lahum 'akhuhum nwh: 'alaa takhshawn allah bitark eibadat ghyrh? 'iiniy lakum rasul 'amin fima ablghkm, fajelu al'iiman wqayt lakum min eadhab allah watyewny fima amrkm bih min eibadatih whdh. wama 'atlub minkum ajrana ealaa tblygh alrsalt, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn, almtsrf fi khlqh, fahdharuu eqabh, watyewny bamtthal awamrh, wajtnab nwahyh"
  26,110,"kadhdhabt qawm nuh risalatan nbyhm, fakanuu bhdha mukadhibin lajamie alrsl; li'ana kl rasul yamur btsdyq jmye alrsl. 'iidh qal lahum 'akhuhum nwh: 'alaa takhshawn allah bitark eibadat ghyrh? 'iiniy lakum rasul 'amin fima ablghkm, fajelu al'iiman wqayt lakum min eadhab allah watyewny fima amrkm bih min eibadatih whdh. wama 'atlub minkum ajrana ealaa tblygh alrsalt, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn, almtsrf fi khlqh, fahdharuu eqabh, watyewny bamtthal awamrh, wajtnab nwahyh"
  26,111,"qal lah qwmh: kayf nsddiqk wntbek, waladhin atabaeuk aradhl alnaas wasaflhm?"